<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Included is a patch that allows this to output without causing progressbar and verbose data to be mixed.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$total = 20;
$progressBar = new Zend_ProgressBar(new Zend_ProgressBar_Adapter_Console(array('output'=&gt;"php://stderr")), 0, $total);
for($i = 1; $i &lt;= $total; ++$i) {
  printf("dumping verbose data\n");
  $progressBar-&gt;update($i);
  usleep(200000);
}
$progressBar-&gt;finish();
</code></pre>

